snippet.title: The Last Orpheus - EEK3 Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Help Orpheus retrieve Eurydice from the depths of Hades in early 2024.

The Last Orpheus is a first-person horror game with music mechanics inspired by Ocarina of Time.
